column5: I have looked at puregas.org website, their app, and online search, but still can't find confirmation of any gas stations in the Sioux Lookout area that sells ethanol free gas that I would prefer to use in my boat. Does anyone know of any locations in this area that sells it?
5 Mile Corner (south of Sioux Lookout) has premium gas without ethanol. Their phone is 807-737-1654
Skywagon beat me to it. Now if they'd put in a diesel pump as well.....
Shell Premium is ethanol free. Lots of Shell stations around.
